This is earth. [[File:Pale_Blue_Dot.png|side|400px]] The Earth is the only world known so far to harbor life. There is nowhere else, at least in the near future, to which our species could migrate. Visit, yes. Settle, not yet. Like it or not, for the moment the Earth is where we make our stand. — Carl Sagan
May this technology, the Aqua Protocol, be used in service of humanity. May it help us to find improved ways of collective sense making. May it help us to collaborate in peace, help us to come to a better understanding how we can preserve conscious and diverse life on planet earth. I believe the Aqua Protocol will act as a new way, how we are sharing information and knowledge. It hopefully allows us to federate a network of trusted information and knowledge, a federated, distributed Wikipedia. Helping humanity to mature to become trusted stewards of planet earth. May it help us to advance our understanding by adventuring out into the solar system to create new colonies on Mars and beyond while we write and preserve a pluralistic history for generations to come.
- 18th January 2022 0xa2026582B94FEb9124231fbF7b052c39218954C2
